    All Classes and Interfaces

    Class
    Description
    Air
    Represents an air-based environment in the ecosystem.
    Algae
    Represents algae as a resource in the ecosystem.
    Bear
    The Bear class represents an omnivorous species in the ecosystem, inheriting from the Omnivore class.
    Canari
    The Canari class represents a herbivorous bird species in the ecosystem.
    Carnivore
    The Carnivore class represents a carnivorous species in the ecosystem.
    Consumable
    Interface representing entities that can be consumed.
    Crow
    The Crow class represents a crow species, which is an omnivore, capable of eating both fruits and other species.
    Ecosystem
    Represents an ecosystem composed of multiple environments and species.
    EcosystemException
    Custom exception class for the ecosystem simulation.
    Environment
    Represents an abstract environment that hosts species and resources.
    Fish
    The Fish class represents a marine herbivore species that consumes algae and moves swiftly in the water.
    Forest
    Represents a forest environment in the ecosystem.
    Fruits
    Represents fruits as a resource in the ecosystem.
    Grass
    Represents grass as a resource in the ecosystem.
    Herbivore
    The Herbivore class represents a herbivorous species in the ecosystem.
    Human
    The Human class represents a human species in the ecosystem.
    MarineHerbivore
    The MarineHerbivore class represents a marine herbivore species in the ecosystem.
    Movable
     
    Ocean
    Represents an ocean environment in the ecosystem.
    Omnivore
    The Omnivore class represents an omnivorous species in the ecosystem.
    Positionn
    Represents a position in a 2D space, defined by x and y coordinates.
    Rabbit
    The Rabbit class represents a herbivorous species of rabbit in the ecosystem.
    Reproducible
    Interface representing entities capable of reproduction.
    Resource
    Abstract class representing a resource in the ecosystem.
    Shark
    The Shark class represents a carnivorous species of shark in the ecosystem.
    Sleepable
    Interface representing the ability for an entity to sleep and wake up.
    Species
    The Species class represents a species in the ecosystem.
    Wolf
    The Wolf class represents a carnivorous species of wolf in the ecosystem.
